{"tid":814751,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想買電子琴或者MIDI鍵盤","createTime":"2018-09-11T12:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T13:58:30.000Z","uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d883fa93d3152e030353039202f555db7cb55ad","tid":814751,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"屋企人淘寶咗啲乜柒手捲鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，玩咗兩下就唔玩<br />\n學睇咗陣五線譜，拎嚟彈咗兩彈，上晒癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但手感同屎無分別<br />\n<br />\n純粹自學消遣下，唔會太深入<br />\n有生之年唔會買鋼琴，間房太細<br />\n所以只可以放係電腦枱彈，61鍵應該夠<br />\n去Tom Lee睇到YAMAHA NP-12 61，2000有找好似幾好<br />\nCASIO都好似唔錯，不過冇見過實物<br />\n<br />\n考慮MIDI係因為可以再細啲，我間房真係轉個身都轉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過MIDI通常都係得10幾20鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a944f821b5fafb057d10b0e84fda350f4f7397","tid":814751,"uid":148076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"電子琴同midi keyboard手感差好遠，建議如果想買嚟彈琴就真係貴少少買翻電子琴，midi keyboard彈到你手都痛"},{"pid":"a1ca3d7b5a55e69a352df66eb3042a2c5269bea3","tid":814751,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9a944f821b5fafb057d10b0e84fda350f4f7397","tid":814751,"uid":148076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"電子琴同midi keyboard手感差好遠，建議如果想買嚟彈琴就真係貴少少買翻電子琴，midi keyboard彈到你手都痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:55:20.000Z","msg":"點解會差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？係咪因為啲人唔預你用MIDI練琴？"},{"pid":"a61e2b0076a838bb44ff307311722506e2bb2641","tid":814751,"uid":148076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1ca3d7b5a55e69a352df66eb3042a2c5269bea3","tid":814751,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9a944f821b5fafb057d10b0e84fda350f4f7397","tid":814751,"uid":148076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T